## Platform hygiene (core-fe)

When you change any matched file:

1. **Read** `agent-os/skills/platform-hygiene/SKILL.md`.
2. **New/renamed/removed env key?** — also read `agent-os/skills/env-schema-add/SKILL.md` and run `pnpm tool:sync-env-example`.
3. **App reads** — use named `platformConfig` flags / `build-env.ts` helpers. Never add raw `import.meta.env.VITE_*`/`DEV`/`PROD`/`MODE` outside the allowlist, and never branch on `platformConfig.environment === '<name>'` (it is a reported value only). Test-runner env needs go through Vite plugins (`plugins/i18n-build.ts`, `plugins/test-env.ts`).
4. **Validators** — run `pnpm validate:vite-env` and `pnpm validate:client-env --production` before finishing.
5. **Dead code** — run `pnpm knip` after removing exports or dependencies.

See **`docs/reference/frontend-platform.md`** and **`docs/deployment/runbooks/environment-variables.md`**.
